"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-product-recommendations-lifestyle-watch-2024-olympics-breaking-online-free-live-stream-1235077201\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByJohn Lonsdale  If you purchase an independently reviewed product or service through a link on our website, Rolling Stone may receive an affiliate commission.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lonsdale_Street\", \"score\": 0.8890279806298286, \"rank\": 0.12482398955721889, \"text\": \"Lonsdale\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lonsdale_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lonsdale_Street\"}, {\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 0.9999999999861302, \"rank\": 1.2962944372098046e-11, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The2024 Summer Olympicsmight be coming to a close this weekend, but one of theParis games' most-anticipated events is just getting started - and (along with a kickoff bySnoop Dogg) making history in the process:breaking, a.k.a, breakdancing.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With this program, we are making the Olympic Games Paris 2024 fit for the post-corona world,\\\" theIOC president previously shared.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is also a strong focus on youth.\\\"\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"B-Boys and B-Girls from around the world - including Team USA'sVictor Montalvo- will help debut breaking at the Place de la Concorde this week for the first time at the 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9948897444692115, \"rank\": 0.004843404873468048, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montalvo_Beach\", \"score\": 0.9955839513879613, \"rank\": 0.0038157784236925434, \"text\": \"Montalvo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montalvo_Beach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montalvo_Beach\"}, {\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999995802682, \"rank\": 4.19755529690107e-10, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only a few events and key moves will help determine medals for the competingbreakdancers.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's how to watch breaking online if you have ditched your cable.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics breaking events air across the E!\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Network and NBC during primetime.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8229494811790984, \"rank\": 0.18280026627765775, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ready to stream all the breaking moments?\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's your guide:    Catch breaking online with aDirecTV Streamsubscription.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streaming service carries local networks, USA Network, as well as E!, so you can stream the Olympic events to catch the B-Boys and B-Girls over the next few days.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.5636098637293567, \"rank\": 0.7742769677291863, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plans start at $79.99 a month, but you can score a free five-day trial to start.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"fuboTVis another great choice for livestreaming Olympics breaking without cable.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscriptions will run you $79.99 a month, and carry local and national networks depending on your location.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We like that it includes a seven-day free trial, making it easy to tune into the remainder of the Paris games without paying a dime.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999758244943, \"rank\": 2.4175568393547944e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Want to watch every breaking event - and the rest of the Paris Olympics?Peacockwill livestream every Olympic event the rest of the weekend before the closing ceremony on Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1756, \"end\": 1770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's affordable at $7.99 a month, and includes access to stream replays and features commentary as well.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3-day Trial  Hulu + Live TVis arguably the best streaming bundle you can get right now, carrying 95 channels as well as access to stream Disney+ and ESPN+.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will get networks including E!\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"and USA Network, plus access to local channels like NBC.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.5636098637293567, \"rank\": 0.7742769677291863, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8229494811790984, \"rank\": 0.18280026627765775, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes with a three-day free trial, then costs $76.99 a month after the trial ends.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sling TV's Blue package carries 46 channels, including the E!\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Network and NBC.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8229494811790984, \"rank\": 0.18280026627765775, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://